<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="merry-adj">merry <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'meri/    美 /'meri/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>愉快的；欢快的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Merry Christmas</strong> to you! 
祝你圣诞快乐!</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Every family in the village is living a merry life. 
村子里家家都过着快乐的生活。</p></div></div>